name: BOJI
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Boji Token was created on 3rd April 2022 with a powerful community which is all open communication for building a better world for stray animals with the partnerships with charities and Non-governmental organizations. The aim is to bring the crypto world and animal lovers together and support all the animals that need helps, feeding the hungry animals and adopt them from the streets and shelters with Boji Token community.
